items.title: TELEOPERADOR/A  ONG. L-V. TARDES 1500 Euros (fijo + Comisión) - ESTABILIDAD
items.requirementMin: -Ganas de crear un impacto positivo en el mundo -Colaborar con los que más lo necesitan -Don de gentes -Habilidades para la comunicación/conversación. -Energía positiva y buen humor -Persistencia y resistencia

items.title: Google Ads & Digital Marketing Specialist
items.requirementMin: Google Ads Certifications (please provide proof of the following): Google Ads Search Certification Google Ads Display Certification Google Ads Video Certification Google Ads Shopping Certification Google Analytics Individual Qualification Fluent in English (written and spoken) Proficiency in WordPress, Shopify, and other content management systems Strong knowledge of digital marketing strategies and tools, including expertise in Twitter, Instagram, and other relevant platforms Experience in creating websites using artificial intelligence-based tools Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills Ability to work independently and as part of a team

items.title: Experienced Attorney with Expertise in Commercial Law, Data Protection, Competition Law, Telecommunication Market Regulation, and Artificial Intelligence
items.requirementMin: Represent the company in complex commercial litigation, data protection, competition law, telecommunication market regulation, and artificial intelligence cases Provide legal advice to the company on European law and regulations Draft and review contracts, agreements, and other legal documents related to the company's operations and business Develop and implement legal strategies for the company's cases and projects Coordinate and communicate with clients, opposing counsel, and court officials Participate in negotiations, settlements, and alternative dispute resolution

items.title: A. Programador/@ Natural/ Adabas
items.requirementMin: Programación Natural/ Adabas, construcción de querys de base de datos, construcción de JCLs. Sus funciones serán toma de requisitos con el cliente u otro analista, análisis de los requisitos, realización de documentación técnica y realización de pruebas funcionales. Perfil funcional, que sepa interpretar las necesidades del cliente. Experiencia al menos 2 /3 años en programación Natural/ Adabas.
